official_title: A bill to permit the Department of Transportation to proceed with a highway project in Lee County, Fla., without regard to section 106 Public Law 89-665 or procedures developed under section 1(3) of Executive Order No. 11593.

summary.text: Permits the Department of Transportation to proceed with a highway project in Lee County, Florida, without following required procedures with respect to historic sites.
